e":"2020-12-29T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"排緊公屋鳩吹姐<br />\n<br />\n起碼2萬up<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6220486688cc733ac01c6d1eb86c837feecd04a","tid":2344961,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:24:15.000Z","msg":"死支那豬即刻死番去支那"},{"pid":"9347fc0d0ee9f53943b011e26404a89dd624013b","tid":2344961,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T08:24:28.000Z","msg":"做官唔係唔記得基層市民，係從來都冇記過基層市民，咪咁天真啦 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}